node.text:
We were fortunate enough to spend a weekend in Yokosuka, Japan entertaining the families living on the base there. We would like to thank the staff of the HMS Albion for their wonderful tour. 
Featuring Dakota Roche, Gary Young, Matthias Dandois, Josh Borden and Omar Hassan.

Video: Colin Mackay

node.text: Perfectly executed to bus to can-can from @Vans_Europe’s @Lara_Lessmann from the video up on @Freedombmx_Mag by @HansFriedrich_. Along with the video, there's an interview with Lara where she explains, “I got my first VANS from my grandpa when I was around 9. In return, I had to bring the newspaper over to him every day during the summer vacation. But I already knew then that the shoe was worth it!”
